OL,3,CMan convicted of 1977 rape after DNA
OL,4,Cbreakthrough
OL,6,FA man has been convicted of raping a
OL,7,Fstudent in Leeds nearly 50 years after
OL,8,Fthe attack following a DNA
OL,9,Fbreakthrough.
OL,11,FDavid Sharp, now aged 66, smashed a
OL,12,Fwindow to get into the woman's room on
OL,13,Fwhat was her first night in the city,
OL,14,Fon 2 October 1977.
OL,16,FHe was wearing a ski mask when he
OL,17,Fsexually assaulted and raped her,
OL,18,Fbefore leaving through the front door
OL,19,Fof the property.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
