OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773436319
OL,3,CMan convicted of 1977 rape after DNA
OL,4,Cbreakthrough
OL,6,FThe offence was reported and
OL,7,Finvestigated at the time, but no
OL,8,Fsuspect was identified.
OL,10,FIt was reinvestigated by the West
OL,11,FYorkshire Police cold case review team
OL,12,Fin 2023.
OL,14,FThey established a DNA profile of the
OL,15,Foffender, but it was not linked to
OL,16,Fanyone on police databases.
OL,18,FHowever, further enquiries led to a
OL,19,Fmatch with one of Sharp's relatives
OL,20,Fand a sample taken from him proved he
OL,21,Fwas the culprit.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773436319
OL,3,CMan convicted of 1977 rape after DNA
OL,4,Cbreakthrough
OL,6,FOfficers later confirmed Sharp, now of
OL,7,FCopland Meadows, Totnes, Devon, was
OL,8,Fliving in Leeds at the time of the
OL,9,Foffence.
OL,11,FHe was found guilty on Friday of one
OL,12,Fcount of rape and one count of
OL,13,Findecent assault following a trial at
OL,14,FLeeds Crown Court and will be
OL,15,Fsentenced on 23 April.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773436319
OL,3,CMan convicted of 1977 rape after DNA
OL,4,Cbreakthrough
OL,6,FDet Sgt Richard Ord, of the major
OL,7,Finvestigation review team, said: "At
OL,8,Fthe heart of this investigation is a
OL,9,Fwoman who has been scarred by the
OL,10,Fevents of 48 years ago for her whole
OL,11,Fadult life. She has told officers that
OL,12,Fshe remembers the crime committed
OL,13,Fagainst her on that day in 1977 like
OL,14,Fit was yesterday.
OL,16,F"Sharp has consistently denied this
OL,17,Foffence and taken no responsibility
OL,18,Ffor his actions. The evidence we were
OL,19,Fable to gather was compelling and has
OL,20,Fresulted in him being convicted of
OL,21,Fthis offence.
OL,26,@oD@bOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773436319
OL,3,CMan convicted of 1977 rape after DNA
OL,4,Cbreakthrough
OL,6,F"No prison sentence can make up for
OL,7,Fthe life term of trauma that the
OL,8,Fvictim has been subjected to, but I
OL,9,Fhope that she feels that some form of
OL,10,Fjustice has now been served."
OL,12,FHe added: "We would encourage anyone
OL,13,Fto come forward who wishes to report
OL,14,Fan offence, no matter how long ago,
OL,15,Fyou will be listened to, this case
OL,16,Fshows time is not a barrier to
OL,17,Fjustice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@KOUyD@IO]
